title: Doctor Who (Includes Specials and Minisodes)
description:
Format: AVI/MP4
Audio: English
Subtitles: N/A

Genre: Sci-Fi, Action, Comedy
Year: 2013
Country: UK | Canada
Producer: Brian Grant, Joe Ahearne, James Hawes, Keith Boak, Euros Lyn
Cast: Christopher Eccleston (The Ninth Doctor), Billie Piper (Rose Tyler), John Barrowman (Captain Jack Harkness), David Tennant (The Tenth Doctor), Catherine Tate (Donna Noble), Freema Agyeman (Martha Jones), Matt Smith (The Eleventh Doctor), Karen Gillan (Amy Pond), Arthur Darvill (Rory Williams), Alex Kingston (River Song), Jenna-Louise Coleman (Clara Oswin Oswald)

Storyline:
The continuing adventures of The Doctor, an alien time traveler - a Time Lord - from Gallifrey. Together with his companions they travel through time and space in the TARDIS, battling evil wherever they can find it.
